# LibrePCB First Project

This project was created as part of my initial hands-on experience with LibrePCB.

## Description
Basic PCB project including:
- Schematic design
- Component placement
- PCB layout

## Purpose
To learn and validate the complete workflow in LibrePCB:
- Library/component usage
- Routing
- Design structure

## Notes
This is a learning project, but it reflects my ability to quickly adopt new EDA tools based on my prior PCB design experience.
